# Prepare the build environment

* [ ] Clone https://github.com/evgeni/pulpcore-packaging
* [ ] [Configure](https://github.com/evgeni/pulpcore-packaging#configure) the build environment
* [ ] [Build](https://github.com/evgeni/pulpcore-packaging#build) the container

# Create/update packages in `foreman-packaging`

* [ ] [Run](https://github.com/evgeni/pulpcore-packaging#run) the container, passing in the configuration and an empty folder that shall contain the results
```
podman run --rm --volume $(pwd)/foreman-packaging/:/app/foreman-packaging/:Z  --env-file packaging.env tfm-pulpcore-builder
```
* [ ] Inspect the generated RPM specs, adjust them if needed
* [ ] Open a PR with the changes
